window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Did I always believe in magic? Not until today. Sure, I had seen my mother's ghost, but I'd managed to rationalize that.</b></p> <p>It wasn't until I was taken to some strange museum in Oregon and inducted into a supernatural agency that I truly believed.</p> <p>Then, something happened to the agency, and I was one of the last mages left in America.</p> <p>Now, I have to learn my peculiar magic all by myself. Well, not entirely by myself. I have a few beautiful women and a disgraced mage genius to help me figure out why my powers are so unique.</p>"; 
